Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十五話\N迷走之旅 御神渡的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.23,0:02:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田忍者群的碉堡在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確位置我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過肯定是在\N很前面的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.54,0:02:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 他們對於神聖的靈藥\N應該知道什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很在意黑騎士團的動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們得到地圖以後\N不可能不展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近真田忍者群的行動很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是因為知道了\N想得到靈藥的黑騎士團的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒體力啦？真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 是肚子好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 彌彥 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發高燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真田的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是獵人叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.17,0:03:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是可疑的壞人\N是因為這孩子突然病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥 你快喝下這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.65,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是喝生水拉肚子\N我再三告訴他要注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.52,0:04:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥一直喝泉水\N說那冰冰的好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.46,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心 喝下那個藥湯\N馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 獵人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我才該驚嚇到你們而道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.27,0:04:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時來路不明的挖金礦的人\N會把這座山搞得亂七八糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔在這座山上生活很久了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這座山上出生長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從祖先開始\N每一代都在這裏當獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.85,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是 你們來深山做什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來尋找神聖的靈藥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們按照這些文句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去調查了諏訪大社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是還是找不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有聽說過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我沒聽過呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.14,0:04:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪大社不光是信州地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它還是日本出名的聖地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在諏訪地方\N有個只有住在山上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代代相傳畏懼敬仰的神聖場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在龍神湖畔的一個神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問這個龍神湖是在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.23,0:05:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比這裏還要深山的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得去查一查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為你們好 還是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.24,0:05:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是山上居民都害怕\N會遭到作祟而不敢靠近的禁地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 作祟這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是迷信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證據是常常在深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從龍神湖的方向\N會傳來可怕的龍叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是我親耳聽見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的照顧 謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 彌彥哪有人\N道謝這麼馬虎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是病人耶！\N你該溫柔一點 醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒用拳頭揍你就不錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥看來是沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.32,0:06:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們特地從東京過來\N我也不好攔阻你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是路上還是請多小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔你也保重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人間處處有溫暖這句話是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大叔幫助我們很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.84,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是能在大叔說的龍神湖神社\N找到新線索就更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好忘記今天的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後你還想平安生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要他們踏入陷阱一步\N就再也無法脫身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.81,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要走去哪裏呀別說是湖了\N連水洼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 應該是這個方向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再走不動的話就把你丟下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水蛭呀水蛭呀水蛭呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水蛭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水蛭常在起霧時出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏一定是龍神湖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼在湖畔應該有神社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N比想像的小確實是神社沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四龍向月亮升起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通往虎口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四龍是指四根御柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.85,0:08:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼向月亮升起是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡的意思也不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.83,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神渡時是指御神渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御神渡是指冬天寒冷的夜裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諏訪湖面的結冰\N發出巨大聲響裂開那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那是冬天耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這點不解呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我們先確認御柱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 大家分頭尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個石碑是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是道祖神嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也有實在有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊也有同樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在神社周圍有四根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說這是御柱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 四龍向月亮升起\N這要怎麼升起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.77,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道有什麼機關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.66,0:09:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以拿下來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 都是你亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀對呀 這一定是作祟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 是月球引力關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大海有漲潮退潮一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是牛頓發現的\N萬有引力的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛頓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,升天之龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.15,0:10:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水開始退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯了 這就是神渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不敢相信我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湖水竟然分成兩半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 這是奇跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這是人為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人故意做的機關\N配合古文獻的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是秘密之門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是虎口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 又要發生什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 進入這地方沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦？是要進去還是撤回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你們不必勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經跟博士約好了\N不能到這裏又空手而回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別只有你自己擺酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還怎麼辦這麼危險\N不能置之不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是該這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.17,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是真正的\N不入虎穴焉得虎子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這裏等於是成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本來解不開謎題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子開始走運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在道場都很神氣的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發抖了 走快點啦 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你別推我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險的彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰\N彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全關起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛 屁股跌得好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你好重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村大色狼 笨蛋 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個洞窟有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有大東西在移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且向這邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有東西向這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被壓扁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快逃會被壓扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼逃 這裏三面都是牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這情況交給我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 剩下的交給我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.94,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要塌陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是土龍閃害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該下手輕一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路有兩條 該往哪邊走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照我在賭場\N鍛練出來的賭徒直覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是無底深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去就沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們走這種路嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許另一條路比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們太天真了不該相信\N左之助的賭徒直覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經你一說我發現\N最近我在賭場常常賭輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在才發現承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.36,0:16:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這並不見得\N另一條路就是安全的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我們就往前走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險哦 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.02,0:16:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那一小塊沒用的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是漢斯博士留下的重要東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋跟命比起來哪一個重要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩個東西是不能比較的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是擔心你耶你講這什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你管啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後再吵啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀現在第一要務是向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方我不敢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.99,0:17:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 讓我來背你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點不好意思問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問就問呀 是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是胖了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.21,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有 沒禮貌 你亂講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你多心了 你太多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你果然胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.23,0:18:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真的能走到\N有神聖的靈藥的地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,類似的情況\N不會一直持續下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前方有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這裏就沒路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.89,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來我們該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段話的下半段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷失於無明黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音之手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將前往大富士的山麓之打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得是這麼記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無明黑暗是指這個洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 觀音的手是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼打開路呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完蛋了這下了真的束手無策了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有查出什麼嗎 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拿這石頭要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這石頭一定有什麼意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點 由太郎\N搞不好是什麼機關哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 什麼也沒發生呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然 那只是沒用的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.03,0:19:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是水滲透進去的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.34,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 看來方向放反了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手是刻向這一邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不像陷阱耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,影子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那地方有觀音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音之手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.37,0:20:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神聖的靈藥在這後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷失於無明黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音之手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將前往\N大富士的山麓之道打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,富士跟長生不老\N的發音相同(富士=不死）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.14,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是指示\N通往神聖靈藥的地方呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶這下子寶物是我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你們還不知道\N那些謎語的全部意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.35,0:21:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑騎士團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人是真田的頭目\N她跟他們聯手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說一切都在我們計劃中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你們也挺有能耐\N打開最後一道門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該向你們道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計劃？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人\N在講什麼莫名奇妙的話呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.41,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼 你講話注意點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道是誰治好你的病的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好像中了敵人陷阱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個老人果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人你是說那獵人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.76,0:21:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長年用槍的獵人身上\N應該有火藥的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.43,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我在那老人身上\N卻什麼也沒感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來那個老人是你偽裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.14,0:22:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說我們不知道\N全部的謎語是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是說博士筆記上那最後一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.68,0:22:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音的手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將前往\N大富士的山麓之道打開吧
